                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18311201-270-off1435 t18311201-270-crimeloc1437"></join>. I put away my coat in the drawer on the 21st of November, and on the 22nd it was missing - the prisoner lodged in the same room with me; I saw my coat again at Worship-street on the Thursday following; the prisoner had lodged there about three months.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18311201-270-person2046">
                  MARY 
                  LIDDINGTON
